CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779282675
OL,3,CMum of missing boy slams 'disgusting'
OL,4,Cfunding disparity with Maddie McCann
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,FThe mother of missing Ben Needham says
OL,8,Fit is "downright disgusting" that the
OL,9,Fsearch for Madeleine McCann has
OL,10,Freceived ten times more funding than
OL,11,Fher son's case.
OL,13,FKerry Needham was speaking after being
OL,14,Fgiven the "heartbreaking" news South
OL,15,FYorkshire Police were scaling back
OL,16,Ftheir involvement in the investigation
OL,17,Finto Ben's disappearance.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779282675
OL,3,CMum of missing boy slams 'disgusting'
OL,4,Cfunding disparity with Maddie McCann
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,FShe said: "It's not right that we've
OL,8,Fhad to sit back and just accept scraps
OL,9,Fof help from the government. My son's
OL,10,Finvestigation in 35 years has had
OL,11,F#1.3million.
OL,13,F"(Madeleine McCann's) case has had
OL,14,Fnearly #14million. How's that fair?
OL,15,FIt's just not, and I won't be silent
OL,16,Fanymore. I am not being critical to
OL,17,Fthe McCanns at all. This is not
OL,18,Fpersonal. This is against the
OL,19,Fgovernment and the authorities`the
OL,20,FBritish government and the authorities.
OL,26,@uD@BpmuD@Upn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779282675
OL,3,CMum of missing boy slams 'disgusting'
OL,4,Cfunding disparity with Maddie McCann
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,F"I'm not going to be quiet about this.
OL,8,FI want the same resources putting into
OL,9,Fmy son's investigation that's put into
OL,10,Fother people's. It's downright
OL,11,Fdisgusting."
OL,13,FBen, from Sheffield, disappeared on
OL,14,Fthe Greek island of Kos in 1991, at
OL,15,Fthe age of 21 months.
OL,17,FDespite one of the longest missing
OL,18,Fperson investigations in British
OL,19,Fhistory - including two excavations at
OL,20,Fthe farmhouse where he was last seen -
OL,21,Fhis whereabouts remain unknown.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779282675
OL,3,CMum of missing boy slams 'disgusting'
OL,4,Cfunding disparity with Maddie McCann
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,FKerry said she had now been informed
OL,8,Fthe South Yorkshire force would no
OL,9,Flonger be responsible for any fresh
OL,10,Finvestigations and would merely pass
OL,11,Fnew information to Interpol and Greek
OL,12,Fpolice.
OL,14,FShe said that while Ben's case was
OL,15,Fbeing sidelined, the search for
OL,16,FMadeleine McCann, who was three when
OL,17,Fshe vanished in Portugal in 2007,
OL,18,Fcontinued to be given a high profile.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779282675
OL,3,CMum of missing boy slams 'disgusting'
OL,4,Cfunding disparity with Maddie McCann
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,F"I've never spoke about this
OL,8,Fpublicly," she added. "I don't deny
OL,9,Fany family of any help, resources to
OL,10,Ffind their loved ones - ever.
OL,12,F"But if you want to, people want to
OL,13,Fcompare the cases, Ben disappeared in
OL,14,FGreece, Madeleine disappeared in
OL,15,FPortugal.
OL,17,F"Madeleine's got the British police
OL,18,Finvolved investigating her
OL,19,Fdisappearance, so how how can they be
OL,20,Fresponsible for it and South Yorkshire
OL,21,FPolice can't? It's so unfair.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779282675
OL,3,CMum of missing boy slams 'disgusting'
OL,4,Cfunding disparity with Maddie McCann
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,F"There's resources being pumped into
OL,8,F(Madeleine's) case every day. Just
OL,9,Frecently, another #100,000 was put
OL,10,Finto that investigation and a team of
OL,11,Fdetectives work solely on that case.
OL,12,FMy SIO (senior investigating officer)
OL,13,Fdoes not work solely on Ben's case,
OL,14,Fhe's got other responsibilities, and
OL,15,Fnow they want to take that away from
OL,16,Fme."
OL,18,FShe added: "South Yorkshire Police are
OL,19,Fmy only lifeline at the moment.
OL,26,@pD@ApmpD@Mpn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779282675
OL,3,CMum of missing boy slams 'disgusting'
OL,4,Cfunding disparity with Maddie McCann
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,F"I've always relied on them to follow
OL,8,Fany investigations, and organise DNA
OL,9,Ftests for me, and pass on any relevant
OL,10,Finformation to whichever country we
OL,11,Freceive that information from.
OL,13,FShe added: "Now, I really do not know
OL,14,Fwhat what's going to happen because I
OL,15,Fcan't see the the Greek authorities
OL,16,Fundertaking any work like that."
OL,18,FKerry said there were plans for the
OL,19,FSIO to go to Kos to meet the Greeks'
OL,20,Fpublic prosecutor and reinterview
OL,21,Fwitnesses.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779282675
OL,3,CMum of missing boy slams 'disgusting'
OL,4,Cfunding disparity with Maddie McCann
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,FShe is now asking Keir Starmer to step
OL,8,Fin.
OL,10,F"I want him to personally intervene,"
OL,11,Fshe said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779282675
OL,3,CMum of missing boy slams 'disgusting'
OL,4,Cfunding disparity with Maddie McCann
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,F"I need more resources. I was quite
OL,8,Fhappy to go along with these plans
OL,9,Fwith South Yorkshire Police, but if
OL,10,Fthis is going to be restricted, and
OL,11,Fthese meetings and these re-interviews
OL,12,Fand witnesses bringing back in are not
OL,13,Fgoing to be conducted by South
OL,14,FYorkshire Police, then I want the
OL,15,FPrime Minister to step in and give me
OL,16,Fresources and or a police force that
OL,17,Fwill, because I am not going to sit
OL,18,Fdown and accept this.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779282675
OL,3,CMum of missing boy slams 'disgusting'
OL,4,Cfunding disparity with Maddie McCann
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,F"I have absolutely up to here with
OL,8,Fsitting and being quiet, and being
OL,9,Fvery diplomatic and not not causing a
OL,10,Fproblem for anyone. I'm going to fight
OL,11,Fthis all the way. This cannot be
OL,12,Fallowed to happen."
OL,14,FIn a statement South Yorkshire Police
OL,15,Fsaid its role had always been a
OL,16,F"conduit for information sharing" with
OL,17,Fthe Greek authorities.
OL,19,F"The investigation itself is led by
OL,20,Fthe Greek authorities," a spokesperson
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779282675
OL,3,CMum of missing boy slams 'disgusting'
OL,4,Cfunding disparity with Maddie McCann
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,F"As we approach the 35 year
OL,8,Fanniversary of the disappearance of
OL,9,FBen, we have reviewed our processes to
OL,10,Fensure these remain fit-for-purpose
OL,11,Fand can withstand any increase in
OL,12,Finformation flow.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779282675
OL,3,CMum of missing boy slams 'disgusting'
OL,4,Cfunding disparity with Maddie McCann
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,F"Our resource allocation has not
OL,8,Fchanged, as we continue to have a
OL,9,Fdesignated family liaison officer and
OL,10,Fdetective inspector as the points of
OL,11,Fcontacts for all of the relevant
OL,12,Fagencies and Ben's family. The Greek
OL,13,Finvestigation is open and we believe
OL,14,Fit will remain open until a conclusion
OL,15,Fis reached.
OL,17,F"Our involvement in support of the
OL,18,Finvestigation has not changed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779282675
OL,3,CMum of missing boy slams 'disgusting'
OL,4,Cfunding disparity with Maddie McCann
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,F"We remain committed to supporting
OL,8,FBen's family and the investigation and
OL,9,Ffully appreciate the distress and
OL,10,Ftrauma the family have been through
OL,11,Fand continue to go through."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G13/13
